# Module Structure and Responsibilities

## Architecture Layers

### Interface Layer ([interface/](mdc:interface))
- HTTP Server handlers
- Request parsing and validation
- SSE (Server-Sent Events) response handling

### Application Layer ([app/](mdc:app))
- Stream processing chain implementation
- Processor plugins coordination
- Business logic orchestration

### Domain Layer ([domain/](mdc:domain))
- Core domain models
- Trait definitions for processors
- Token provider interfaces
- Internal event structures

### Infrastructure Layer ([infra/](mdc:infra))
- LLM API client implementations
- Token provider implementations
- Concrete processor implementations
- External service integrations

### Binary Layer ([binary/](mdc:binary))
- Application entry points
- Configuration loading
- Service bootstrapping

## Key Abstractions
- Processor Chain: Pluggable stream processors for message transformation
- TokenProvider: Authentication token management system
- StreamForwarder: LLM API communication handler
- InternalStreamEvent: Standardized message format
